Known by its ticker symbol ARKK, Wood=E2=80=99s fund became an investor dar=
ling shortly after the onset of the Covid-19 pandemic with hugely successfu=
l bets on unprofitable and =E2=80=9Cdisruptive=E2=80=9D technology companie=
s. It took in huge amounts of investor money, culminating with a $6.5 billi=
on inflow in the first quarter of 2021, when its share price peaked.
