 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  times</a> around <a=
 href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32105300.262411/aHR0=
cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDYtMjkvdGhlLWJ=
pZy1iYW5rcy1hcmVuLXQtc3RyZXNzZWQ_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDcxNzIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX2=
