 but that does not work for investing. The best time to buy into a big inve=
sting trend is just before it becomes a big investing trend, and the worst =
time is at the peak. Anyway here=E2=80=99s a story about Cathie Wood=E2=80=
=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32105300.2624=
11/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9pbnZlc3RvcnMtYXJlLWJhaWxpbmctb24t=
