 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;"> vending-machine challenge</a>, but this approach is both healthier and =
more permanent.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-3" style=3D"co=
