<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The trio struck again a year later, when Citig=
roup Inc. stock fell below $1.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One of Davidov=E2=80=99s $2 bills was torn in =
half and taped to the door of the bank=E2=80=99s midtown skyscraper, and Mc=
Daniel again sent an image to <em>Dealbreaker</em>.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">While it was published, the second prank didn=
=E2=80=99t gain the same traction.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It certainly did not.=C2=A0<em>I=C2=A0</em>rem=
ember seeing that and thinking it was a brilliant callback, but in the inte=
