=E2=80=99s positive or negative results,=E2=80=9D Kumar told Endpoints. =E2=
=80=9CIt has everything to do with the concept of wandering, and the pain a=
nd the suffering that=E2=80=99s required to go on one of these epic journey=
s.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
